cs.CL, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with sentiment analysis using text embeddings.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with multi-modal embeddings using audio and video views/modes of data.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses Deep Canonical Correlation Analysis (DCCA) to combine the features from different views/modes.
- cs.SD (Sound) is relevant as the paper deals with audio data.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with classification tasks on benchmark datasets.
